dct_title_s: A MAP OF THE WORLD. Shewing the Course of Mr. DAMPIERS Voyage Round it: From 1679. to 1691
dct_description_sm: Issued in: A Collection of Voyages. In Four Volumes. / by William Dampier. -- London : Printed for James and John Knapton, at the Crown in St. Paul’s Church-Yard. MDCCXXIX (1729).
In English, with title as in State 1. H. Moll Fecit (bottom center). Damp. Voy. Vol. I. Plate 1. (lower left). To face the Title. (lower right).
California with two northern indented bays. The S. of Annian is lightly drawn to the north of the island. Shows the track of Dampier’s voyage.
